snippet.title: Lemmings: 3DO (1994)
snippet.description:
Intro and gameplay from Lemmings on the 3DO, released in 1994.
Developed by DMA Design and published by Psygnosis.

Game credits:
- Brian Johnston - Music
- Brian Watson - Code
- Colin Anderson - Music
- Doug Smith - Code
- Gary Timmons - Animation
- John Whyte - Code
- Martin Good - 3D Movie
- Scott Johnston - Graphics
- Stacey Jamieson - 3D Movie
- Tim Wright - Music

Watch other editions of the Lemmings game here:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLW_a1Ic-Y4n_sYe2n1OCwe0j03EOxxq3U

Enjoy the video? Remember to like, comment and subscribe to Retro Gaming TV - http://bit.ly/2N5gjMA
